d? Contact us.\",\n    \"contact_support_cta\": \"Contact support\",\n    \"faq\": {\n      \"how_quick_request\": {\n        \"q\": \"How does Quick Request work?\",\n        \"a\": \"Describe your problem in one tap — the system finds the nearest available mechanic within 30 seconds and shows price and ETA.\"\n      },\n      \"who_master\": {\n        \"q\": \"Who are these mechanics?\",\n        \"a\": \"All mechanics are verified: documents, experience, reviews from real customers. We only show certified workshops.\"\n      },\n      \"price_calc\": {\n        \"q\": \"How is the price calculated?\",\n        \"a\": \"Price is fixed before work starts. The mechanic sees your problem and location and gives a flat rate. No hidden fees.\"\n      },\n      \"cancel_request\": {\n        \"q\": \"Can I cancel?\",\n        \"a\": \"Yes — free of charge before the mechanic arrives. After arrival, a call-out fee may apply (shown in the request).\"\n      },\n      \"contact_master\": {\n        \"q\": \"How do I contact the mechanic?\",\n        \"a\": \"Once your request is accepted, chat and call buttons appear. Contact stays available until job completion.\"\n      },\n      \"safety\": {\n        \"q\": \"Is it safe?\",\n        \"a\": \"All payments go through secure escrow. Funds are released to the mechanic only after you confirm the work is done.\"\n      },\n      \"payment\": {\n        \"q\": \"How do I pay?\",\n        \"a\": \"Card, Apple Pay or Google Pay in the app. No need to hand cash to the mechanic.\"\n      },\n      \"reviews\": {\n        \"q\": \"How do I leave a review?\",\n        \"a\": \"After job completion you'll get a notification. Rate the mechanic 1–5 stars and add a short comment.\"\n      }\n    }\n  },\n  \"support\": {\n    \"title\": \"Contact Support\",\n    \"intro\": \"Describe your issue — we reply within 24 hours.\",\n    \"email\": \"Email\",\n    \"call\": \"Call\",\n    \"subject_label\": \"Subject\",\n    \"subject_placehol